description: Wholly Kabob is a tasty kabob trailer serving Persian-style grilled kabob skewers to the Austin streets. The kabobs are served on wheat or white pita bread, with toppings including shallots and yogurt sauce, avocado/jalapeño sauce, spicy mustard sauce, freshly-made hummus, and much more! If your mouth's watering at the sound of these delicious bites, stop by Wholly Kabob today!
name: Wholly Kabob
